node.text:
WIN $1000 or a camera, EVERY WEEK! Hands up for the #Insta360HighFive Challenge! 🤚 🌍

1️⃣ Create a video using ANY camera or phone, with at least one high five transition
2️⃣ Follow @insta360 on Instagram
3️⃣ Post your video with: 
#Insta360HighFive + @insta360 + tag one friend
4️⃣ Win 💰 / 📷

Challenge is live from Sep 15 to Oct 6. Good luck!

node.text:
The new residential Mega Yacht ‘Somnio’ will be the largest yacht in the world when it launches in 2024. 🔥

This 728 feet mansion will have 39 apartments across 6 floors, with apartment prices starting from $11,000,000 with an invite only to purchase. The cost of the project is to be around $600,000,000 and it will be built in Norway. 🛥

Photos by: @winchdesign_wd

node.text:
Congratulations to @tracy_louise_cartledge on winning this giveaway with @trendingtravel.co.uk 🥳 

☀️✈️WIN A 5-NIGHT STAY IN CRETE FOR 2 AT @domes_resorts, FLIGHTS AND TRANSFERS INCLUDED✈️☀️
We’re so excited to treat one of our lucky followers to ANOTHER special holiday😍Get ready to top up your tan with your chance to win a 5-night stay for 2 people at the breath-taking @domes_resorts Domes of Elounda, Autograph Collection in Crete @domesofelounda, Half Board with flights and transfers included✨ PLUS, @misscallyjane STAYED HERE... Want to holiday like her? Find out how to win below👀❤️

To be in with a chance of winning✈️✨
-Like this post
-Tag the person you would take with you
-Follow @trendingtravel.co.uk, @domes_resorts & @misscallyjane

DON’T FORGET... Each new tag is an additional entry into the competition too👀

Want to really be seen? Share this post to your story & show us some love on our recent posts as well🔥

This competition will close at 23:59 16/09/2021🙌

Please be aware of fake accounts trying to contact you during the competition. This is our only official page and the winner will be announced via our story on 17th September 2021. T&C’s will be available at trendingtravel.co.uk/competition
